
Types of resource meta Argument use in terraform .

depends_on = To handle hidden resource or module dependenices that terraform can't automatically infer.

count = For creating multiple resources instances according to a count .

for_each = To create multiple instances accoding to a map , or set of strings .

Provider = For selecting a non default provider configuration .

lifecycle = Standard Resource behaviour can be altered using special nested lifecycle block within a resource block body .

Provisioners and Connections = For taking extra actions after resource creation .

   